FBIS3-16156 "drsov049_b_94005" FBIS-SOV-94-049 Document Type:Daily Report 14 Mar 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Yeltsin Reportedly Meets, Reassures Yerin LD1103213294 Moscow 2x2 Television in Russian 2040 GMT 11 Mar 94 LD1103213294 Moscow 2x2 Television Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] A correspondent of the Postfactum agency has learned from confidential sources in the Russian Ministry of Internal Affairs that a closed door meeting has recently taken place between President Boris Yeltsin and Internal Affairs Minister Viktor Yerin. The source said that Boris Yeltsin estimated the activity of the Ministry at the present moment as satisfactory and promised all kinds of support for the law enforcement bodies.
